Intrebari operare clasa IV v.3.32, versiune actualizata pe <a href="http://examyo.scienceontheweb.net">http://examyo.scienceontheweb.net</a> <font color="#FAFAFA"><curricula>prog_CEPT_Entry_op</curricula></font>
